OL,5, Amazon has said it will spend several  
OL,6, billion dollars to manage labour       
OL,7, shortages and supply chain issues in   
OL,8, the run-up to Christmas.               
OL,10,FThe online retail giant said it was    
OL,11,Fdoing "whatever it takes to minimise   
OL,12,Fthe impact" on customers and sellers.  
OL,14,FMeanwhile, Apple said a shortage of    
OL,15,Fsemiconductor chips had cost it $6bn   
OL,16,F(#4.35bn) in lost sales.               
OL,18,FThe tech giant's boss, Tim Cook,       
OL,19,Fadmitted its problems would persist    
OL,20,Fover the festive period.               
